Before finalizing, verify:

- The projection contains new-epic authoring semantics only.
- No new epic proposal is included.
- No repository state is included.
- No roadmap completion state is included.
- No completed epic history is included.
- No epic is authored.
- Every retained statement helps author a first authoritative epic from a strategic opportunity.
