- Strategic opportunity preservation is explicit.
- Desired capability semantics are explicit.
- Repository grounding rules are explicit.
- Abstraction selection rules are explicit.
- Scope derivation rules are explicit.
- Dependency derivation rules are explicit.
- Milestone derivation rules are explicit.
- Constraint integration is explicit.
- Blocking rules are explicit.
- Traceability requirements are explicit.
- Canonical vocabulary is preserved.
- Excluded operational, implementation, validation, realignment, reimagination, and prioritization details are not present.
- The projection is compact enough to be passed into CreateNewEpic.
